{"tid":1193291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周浩鼎憂觸發公屋領養法律挑戰","createTime":"2019-06-08T23:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T00:32:13.000Z","uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"15dcbfec3c2a7fe3d4d41da747310dcdcc4e9365","tid":1193291,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:39:03.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】終院裁定公務員同性配偶可享已婚公務員福利及合併報稅，民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎昨日表示，因應該案裁決，擔心在外地結婚的同性配偶回港後領養小孩一旦被拒，或會觸發下一輪法律挑戰。他形容這對本港社會的家庭制度造成「非常翻天覆地的變化」。<br />\n<br />\n節錄<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190608/s00002/1559933243353/%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E6%86%82%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00002%2F1559933243353%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E%25E6%2586%2582%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%2588%25B0&d=%2BD6XGwqev%2FlZKpArKwvoHeDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=5b5a0d2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190608%2Fs00002%2F1559933243353%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%25B5%25A9%25E9%25BC%258E%25E6%2586%2582%25E8%25A7%25B8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B1%258B%25E9%25A0%2598%25E9%25A4%258A%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%2588%25B0&h=6e020de4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190608/s00002/1559933243353/%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E6%86%82%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E5%85%AC%E5%B1%8B%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%8A%E6%B3%95%E5%BE%8B%E6%8C%91%E6%88%B0</a><br />\n<br />\n單程證，假結婚有天敵了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808